rows.label: qst650204_msg0001
rows.name:
Tora.
It look like you found what I hoped.

rows.label: qst650204_msg0002
rows.name: Now do you believe me?

rows.label: qst650204_msg0004
rows.name: What wrong, Tora?

rows.label: qst650204_msg0005
rows.name:
Did Tora forget bygone days when
we worked together so passionately
with Sonnypon Tatezo?

rows.label: qst650204_msg0006
rows.name: Tora not forget!

rows.label: qst650204_msg0007
rows.name: You real Grampypon Senzo!

rows.label: qst650204_msg0008
rows.name: Meh meh! Toraaa!

rows.label: qst650204_msg0009
rows.name: You real biggipon now, Tora.

rows.label: qst650204_msg0010
rows.name: Taller than Senzo!

rows.label: qst650204_msg0011
rows.name: Thanks to eat Tasty Sausage every day!

rows.label: qst650204_msg0012
rows.name: Tasty Sausage...every day... Ew.

rows.label: qst650204_msg0013
rows.name: Anyway, that enough reunioning.

rows.label: qst650204_msg0014
rows.name: There special important task to do.

rows.label: qst650204_msg0015
rows.name:
Did Tora input Blade data into Hana
like Senzo write in letter?

rows.label: qst650204_msg0016
rows.name:
Yes! With help from friends, Tora
collected all data.

rows.label: qst650204_msg0017
rows.name:
But why Grampypon need such
battle data?

rows.label: qst650204_msg0018
rows.name: It for benefit friends of Tora.

rows.label: qst650204_msg0019
rows.name: But how it help Boss...?

rows.label: qst650204_msg0020
rows.name: Hana, please come with Senzo!

rows.label: qst650204_msg0021
rows.name: Masterpon, permission to go...?

rows.label: qst650204_msg0022
rows.name: It okay, Hana. Follow Grampypon!

rows.label: qst650204_msg0023
rows.name:
Understood. If situation become
uncomfortable, Hana will activate
Stranger Danger protocol immediately.

rows.label: qst650204_msg0024
rows.name: Why assume such thing of Grampypon?!

rows.label: qst650204_msg0025
rows.name: Is Hana really gonna be okay...?

rows.label: qst650204_msg0026
rows.name:
Tora have no idea what big idea is.
But Tora trust Grampypon.
Hope that is not big mistake...

rows.label: qst650204_msg0027
rows.name:
Knowing what I do of your
grandfather's proclivities, Tora...
perhaps you are right to doubt...
